01:25:18.036 --> 01:25:19.038
Aaw!

01:25:24.910 --> 01:25:25.877
I'm back.

01:25:27.045 --> 01:25:28.114
Thanks to Renzulli.

01:25:33.018 --> 01:25:34.487
Has anything changed?

01:25:35.554 --> 01:25:36.522
No.

01:25:37.723 --> 01:25:39.792
But this allows us
to fight another day.

